question: Which restaurant can I find when moving towards Johnsonburg Swamp Preserve, Johnsonburg, NJ within 150 kilometers from False Flag, Long Island City, NY?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.948714 40.748971)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-74.867494 40.980105)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.948714 40.748971)',4326)::geography, 150000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.948714 40.748971)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
